# Implementation Plan - Show Mood and Stress Progress Trends

Add interactive, accessible tooltip overlays, keyboard-navigable focus targets, screen-reader details, and visual guide lines on hover/focus to the `Weekly mood pulse` SVG chart. Expand backend tests to verify trend aggregation.

## User Review Required

> [!NOTE]
> We will add an interactive hover & focus overlay system in React. When a student hovers over or focuses a data point:
> - A dashed vertical line aligns with the date column.
> - A premium HTML floating tooltip appears above the date, showing detailed averages for Mood, Stress, and Energy.
> - Keyboard users can press `Tab` to navigate through individual date columns on the chart.
>
> We will add backend tests in `service_test.go` to explicitly verify the math of daily averages (mood, stress, energy) and sorting of trend points.

